span(
  ng-if = "!isConfirmation && (currentOrg.poppa.isInTrial() || currentOrg.poppa.isInActivePeriod())"
) At your current usage, you’ll be charged for the {{planMapping[plan.id]}} plan at ${{calculatePlanPrice() | centsToDollars}} for {{plan.userCount}} users.
  strong.strong(
    ng-if = "currentOrg.poppa.isInTrial()"
  ) &#32;You will not be charged until your trial ends.

span(
  ng-if = "currentOrg.poppa.isGraceExpired() || currentOrg.poppa.isInGrace() && currentOrg.poppa.hasPaymentMethod"
) You’ll be charged&#32;
  strong ${{calculatePlanPrice() | centsToDollars}}
  | &#32;for {{plan.userCount}} users.

span(
  ng-if = "isConfirmation && currentOrg.poppa.isInActivePeriod() && paymentMethod"
) You’ve been charged&#32;
  strong ${{calculatePlanPrice() | centsToDollars}}
  | &#32;for {{plan.userCount}} users.

span(
  ng-if = "showNext"
) &#32;Your {{currentOrg.poppa.isInTrial() ? 'first' : 'next'}} billing date is {{getTrialEndDate()}}.
